 compelling workshops. With an end-to-end templated structure, we guide you on topics such as facilitating needs analyses, understanding learners' needs, and managing tough topics, our course empowers trainees to become successful trainers themselves. The beauty of our train-the-trainer course is that it is not industry-specific. This allows you to understand delivering courses across various industries and sectors comprehensively. You will acquire the skills to design and effectively deliver training courses while also developing your own personal style as a trainer. </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-eJwWfJ hSzDKM pf-29_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-31_">Career opportunities </span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Career_Opportunities_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1691758125" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Career_Opportunities_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1691758125 1536w" width="2507" height="1643" alt="Career Opportunities - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Career Opportunities - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jOxtWs ffIUiZ pf-32_"/><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-33_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-35_">Upon successful completion of the course, you will have a variety of career opportunities available to you. Here are some avenues you can explore: </span></p><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hiwPVj bcyuPn pf-36_">Freelance trainer</h3><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-38_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-40_">Work independently and design and deliver your own training courses. With the knowledge and skills gained from our train-the-trainer course, you can create and deliver customised workshops catering to your expertise and clients' needs. </span></p><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hiwPVj bcyuPn pf-41_">Professional training provider</h3><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-43_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-45_">Collaborate with established training providers and deliver courses on their behalf. By registering with recognised training organisations, you can leverage their reputation and resources to reach a wider audience and expand your training portfolio. </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-eJwWfJ hSzDKM pf-46_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-48_">Wide range of learners</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Wide_range_of_learners_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1691758198" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Wide_range_of_learners_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1691758198 1536w" width="2000" height="1333" alt="Wide range of learners - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Wide range of learners - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jOxtWs ffIUiZ pf-49_"/><p class="sc-ljMRFG jiRhOP pf-50_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-52_">Our train-the-trainer course attracts learners from diverse backgrounds and age groups, including nurses, office staff, and individuals seeking personal growth and career development. There are no specific entry requirements, making it accessible for anyone looking to take on a new challenge and boost their confidence.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-eJwWfJ hSzDKM pf-53_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-eZKLwX jcZVJU pf-55_">Application of skills</span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Application_of_Skills_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1691758294" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Application_of_Skills_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1691758